description: The fund seeks to match the performance of the Solactive GBS Developed Markets ex United States Large & Mid Cap Index NTR. Provides investors with broad exposure to international stocks (stocks outside the U.S.). Employs a passively managed, low-cost index approach with a fully transparent portfolio. Is highly liquid so investors can buy or sell any time the stock market is open.
name: BNY Mellon International Equity ETF
